sequenceDiagram
    participant Src as Log Source
    participant KF as Kinesis Firehose
    participant OS as OpenSearch
    participant S3 as S3 Data Lake
    participant User as Analyst

    Src->>KF: Send logs
    KF->>KF: Buffer & transform
    KF->>OS: Index recent logs
    KF->>S3: Archive all logs
    User->>OS: Search recent logs
    OS-->>User: Results
    User->>S3: Query historical (Athena)
    S3-->>User: Results
